{"tid":1074573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「求救」屋企人遇到寶藥黨","createTime":"2019-03-23T13:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T01:12:38.000Z","uid":224861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"894d52a757ccb2edd8ff1817c76bd47cf50fb7b0","tid":1074573,"uid":224861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"早兩日同老豆傾計<br />\n佢唔知係邊識到條友介紹左隻藥俾佢，<br />\n係醫坐骨神經，痛風症果d<br />\n講到好撚勁好撚神奇<br />\n一聽到已經心知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再傾落去，佢話粒藥人地賣$180@1俾佢<br />\n佢買撚左8粒，差唔多$1500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我叫佢拎岀黎睇<br />\n結果拎岀黎個包裝係咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeH3sRQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeH3sRQ.png&h=a1540437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乜撚野成份資料包裝都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjGPoqv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjGPoqv.png&h=1bcf0507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢盒唔知乜野黎，冇問佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqB4ci4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqB4ci4.png&h=53b3f057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢粒就係賣$180既神藥，成粒防潮珠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打開入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpMr958.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpMr958.png&h=62d7ac7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聞落係有中藥味，但睇落真係好撚流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我問佢食撚完有咩咁神奇呀？<br />\n佢話食完覺得全身血氣通左，<br />\n又通左便咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我語重心長咁同佢講，不明來歷既藥唔好食<br />\n咩成份藥性都唔撚知，有起事上黎追究唔到<br />\n佢仲要話會有咩事姐，咪中藥囉，有中藥味<br />\n甘甘地，然後仲即刻係我面前啪左粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢又話自己唔係信到十足，依加買幾粒試下咋嘛<br />\n試過好既可以賣岀去當幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經軟硬都試過哂，都唔撚聽我講<br />\n有冇巴絲有同樣經歷，請教大家點樣拉返我老豆岀火坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60662864846a46286f5a31a51416b77e53c1e9bf","tid":1074573,"uid":207844,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bc63b1d2ae6334ad789b50ed81ad8a4ee350c68","tid":1074573,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"圖一咁似魚糧"},{"pid":"70725b4931521f7dc7b953d5cf75482c08647ff3","tid":1074573,"uid":224861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc63b1d2ae6334ad789b50ed81ad8a4ee350c68","tid":1074573,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"圖一咁似魚糧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"係好似，聞落都係中藥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784d4e50384bc7d9a8424537114fc4def1ddfc58","tid":1074573,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"點你諗住點"},{"pid":"49ea5f7cdbf4038d0c269b614c393ea44f2b1fb6","tid":1074573,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"比集警訊佢睇啦"},{"pid":"e516388911985d00d73394f6467c794293fa9806","tid":1074573,"uid":236691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"無用嘅，呢啲情況你反駁佢只會搞到佢更加相信啲藥有效，人就係咁，一定要出事先知錯嘅"},{"pid":"b4e3d3fab1778edb2e80d87a058555114e2f75fe","tid":1074573,"uid":224861,"like":0,"disl